39:25.864 --> 39:28.033
don't just show up at my door.

39:28.066 --> 39:32.070
Oh... okay.

39:32.103 --> 39:35.140
Yeah, okay, cool.

39:35.173 --> 39:37.909
Um, so could you go?

39:37.943 --> 39:40.546
I-I-I have something
I need to do.

39:40.579 --> 39:42.648
Are you kicking me out?

39:44.550 --> 39:47.453
Lil' bit.

39:47.486 --> 39:49.054
Bye, Josh.

39:57.996 --> 40:00.699
(door opens and closes)

40:00.732 --> 40:04.169
I'm sorry, Channy bear.

40:14.580 --> 40:15.781
Hey, what's going on?

40:15.814 --> 40:16.948
Hi.

40:16.982 --> 40:19.050
You okay? What...

40:20.586 --> 40:21.787
No, I c... I-I can't do this.

40:21.820 --> 40:24.055
I-I can't eat a dusty potato.

40:24.089 --> 40:25.724
Oh, God, is that
what I taste like?

40:25.757 --> 40:28.059
I mean, I, I ate a,
an old French fry

40:28.093 --> 40:29.528
off the floor of my car,
but I sh...

40:29.561 --> 40:30.829
It's a metaphor.
Wa... you did what?

40:30.862 --> 40:31.930
It doesn't matter.

40:32.898 --> 40:34.199
No, good God, stop, woman.

40:34.232 --> 40:36.134
Greg, listen to me.

40:36.167 --> 40:38.537
This isn't about
anyone else but you.

40:38.570 --> 40:39.905
Okay?

40:39.938 --> 40:41.873
You're not second choice.

40:41.907 --> 40:43.775
I promise.

40:48.714 --> 40:49.915
Listen, if this
is going to happen,

40:49.948 --> 40:51.717
you need to know
something.
Okay.

40:51.750 --> 40:53.819
This isn't going to be like a
roll in the hay and you go home.

40:53.852 --> 40:55.186
This is going to be
like three days

40:55.220 --> 40:57.823
of you and me just
ruining each other.

40:57.856 --> 40:59.558
And not emotionally.

40:59.591 --> 41:00.859
Is that what you want?

41:00.892 --> 41:03.862
When do we start?

41:03.895 --> 41:06.097
*

41:19.845 --> 41:21.513
I'm so glad we're
finally doing this.

41:21.547 --> 41:22.714
Me, too.

41:22.748 --> 41:24.683
I mean, there's so many girls
I could have brought here,

41:24.716 --> 41:25.817
like a whole bunch,

41:25.851 --> 41:27.619
but I chose you, Ashley.

41:27.653 --> 41:29.788
It's Ally.
Don't care.

41:30.722 --> 41:33.659
Can we have sex now? Yay.

41:33.692 --> 41:35.026
Oh, my God.

41:35.060 --> 41:36.194
You're an idiot.

41:36.227 --> 41:38.697
And you're horrible.

41:38.730 --> 41:42.634
Why do I always make the same
mistake over and over again?

41:42.668 --> 41:44.035
I make terrible decisions.

41:44.069 --> 41:45.971
I go for the
lowest form of man

41:46.004 --> 41:47.739
because I'm afraid
to be with someone

41:47.773 --> 41:48.874
I might actually connect with.

41:48.907 --> 41:50.642
You know what?
Screw this.

41:50.676 --> 41:52.644
I'm going back
to nursing school.

41:52.678 --> 41:54.279
Wait, do you want me
to do another cartwheel?

41:54.312 --> 41:55.681
I'm-I'm-I'm good at those.

41:55.714 --> 41:57.683
Whatever.

41:57.716 --> 41:59.718
She'll be back.

41:59.751 --> 42:00.686
They always come back.

